<!--
  m3-expressive Phase D.4 — accent-coloured glyph for the
  `MediaLibraryService` "Currently listening" browse-tree root in
  Android Auto. Wired through `MediaMetadata.Builder.setArtworkUri(...)`
  in WhisperboyLibrarySessionCallback. Material `play_circle_filled`
  vector path; fill tone matches `PlaybackAccent.onContainer`
  (0xFFFFB877) — the orange "in motion" accent reused from the
  per-category palette in `theme/CategoryAccent.kt`. Auto's system
  theme generally re-tints media-browse artwork monochrome on most
  head units; the colour is a best-effort signal for renderers that
  honour it.
-->
